            On <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">Jan. 18</TIMEX>, amid revelations that his <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Christian Democratic Union</ENAMEX> accepted
<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">2.4 million deutsche marks</NUMEX> (<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">$1.2 million</NUMEX>) in secret contributions, former
